Class ServerUpgradeResponseImpl

All Implemented Interfaces:
Content.Sink, Response, ServerUpgradeResponse
public class ServerUpgradeResponseImpl extends Response.Wrapper implements ServerUpgradeResponse
Upgrade response used for websocket negotiation. Allows setting of extensions and subprotocol without using headers directly.
